Global Satellite IoT Market Insights
Satellite IoT Market size was valued at USD 5.3 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 12.4 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 12.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Satellite IoT Market Overview
The Satellite IoT market is experiencing significant growth due to its increasing demand across industries for seamless, reliable, and global connectivity. The global market size for Satellite IoT was valued at approximately USD 7.5 billion in 2024, and it is projected to expand at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 24.8% from 2025 to 2030, reaching an estimated value of USD 33.5 billion by 2030. This growth is primarily driven by the expanding IoT ecosystem and the need for connectivity in remote, underserved regions.

